====== Read Me ======

===== Running the simulation =====

Use the following command:

<code sh>
> ./ogensim EXEC -p PROC -m MEM
</code>

Where:
  * EXEC is the path to the executable binary,
  * PROC is the path to the OTAWA XML description of the pipeline,
  * MEM is the path to the OTAWA XML description of the memory.

LPC2138 example of PROC and MEM is given in proc.xml and mem.xml.
